 NOLLYWOOD actress, Opeyemi Ayeola has offered advice to men looking to get married. The thespian and mother of two advises that it is better to marry a single mother with upto three kids than a pretender who has had multiple abortions. Ayeola took to her Instagram page to share her opinion with thousands of her fans and followers on the platform. She wrote, “Better marry a truthful after 2 or 3 or more than marry a lady with 7 abortions pretending to be an angel yet she’s a mother of graves… Unknown”. Opeyemi is one of the few lucky actors who made a good return to Nollywood after she left for the United Kingdom immediately she got married in 2007 at the peak of her career.